api_list.name: Get Fake Full Name
api_list.description: Endpoint to get a fake full name.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://fake-information-generator.p.rapidapi.com/fake/full-name"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "fake-information-generator.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
